      "title": "payment_read_models Size (table vs indexes)",
      "description": "Heap, index, and search-index size for payment_read_models. Sustained growth in the GIN search index relative to table size is an early signal that full-text search may be approaching the point where Postgres alone is no longer the right tool (see H6 decision criteria).",
